etycenter" class="footerlink">Safety</a><a data-track="footer-blog" href="../blog/discord-activities-play-games-and-watch-together" class="footerlink">Blog</a><a data-track="footer-feedback" href="https://feedback.discord.com/" class="footerlink">Feedback</a><a data-track="footer-developers" href="../build" class="footerlink">Developers</a><a data-track="streamkit" href="../brand-new/streamkit" class="footerlink">StreamKit</a></div><div id="w-node-aa4f1aec-51b3-2181-ee4b-e8a408a59c60-08a59c32" class="footerlinks"><h3 class="heading">Policies</h3><a data-track="footer-terms" id="w-node-aa4f1aec-51b3-2181-ee4b-e8a408a59c63-08a59c32" href="../terms" class="footerlink">Terms</a><a data-track="footer-privacy" href="https://discord.com/privacy" class="footerlink">Privacy</a><a data-track="footer-guidelines" href="https://discord.com/guidelines" class="footerlink">Guidelines</a><a data-open-cookie-settings="true" data-track="cookie-settings" href="community-management-the-basics#" class="footerlink">Cookie Settings</a><a data-track="footer-acknowledgments" href="https://discord.com/acknowledgements" class="footerlink">Acknowledgments</a><a data-track="footer-licenses" href="https://discord.com/licenses" class="footerlink">Licenses</a></div></div><div class="footerbottomseparator"></div><div class="footerbottom"><a data-track-nav="footer-discord-home-logo" href="http://://discord.com/" class="w-inline-block"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/6238e97f6441e30a13a52345/623b7075128add6f2a776877_DiscordLogo.svg" loading="lazy" alt=""/></a><a id="login-or-open-button" data-track-nav="navbar-login-button" href="https://discord.com/register" class="button login-button-blurple open-or-signup-js w-button">Sign up</a></div></div></div></footer><script src="https://d3e54v103j8qbb.cloudfront.net/js/jquery-3.5.1.min.dc5e7f18c8.js?site=6238e97f6441e30a13a52345" type="text/javascript" integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0=" crossorigin="anonymous"></